instances.text: You can change the scaling of the font: fontScaleWidth: 75% = narrow / condensed 125% = wide / extended 250% = super extended fontScaleHeight: 75% = short 125% = tall 250% = super tall
instances.untaggedText:
You can change the scaling of the font:

            fontScaleWidth:
            75% = narrow / condensed
            125% = wide / extended
            250% = super extended

            fontScaleHeight:
            75% = short
            125% = tall
            250% = super tall
